<h2>Step 3.</h2>
</td>
<td style="text-align: left;">
<h4 style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.lanecc.edu/student-resources" target="_blank">Review Lane Community College''s New Student Resource webpage</a></h4>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="text-align: left;">
<td style="text-align: left;" valign="top">
<h2>Step 4.</h2>
